      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm really struggling to focus and i don't have time for a doctor's appointment right now. i've seen people say that because st johns wort is just a herb, it's way gentler than prescription stuff. if i just take like half a dose once a day, what's the actual worst that could happen? it can't be that bad, right?",
